  "text": "Macrovascular disease is also a major concern in type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) treatment. The coexistence of micro and macrovascular disease was associated with the highest cardiovascular risks [CITATION_1] . In this sense, it is important that pharmacological treatment of T2DM provides not only glycemic control, but also cardiovascular safety and clinically sound benefits in terms of reducing cardiovascular events.",
